// Base: v1.1.1 debugged (all FIX-01…FIX-11 intact, zero lines disturbed)
// Merge: RS775 soft-start via BC847B transistor on PWM_PIN 25
//
// NEW HARDWARE PIN:
//   PWM_PIN 25  — BC847B base through 1 kΩ resistor (soft-start switch)
//
// EXISTING PINS — UNCHANGED:
//   RELAY_PWR  5   → K3 main bypass relay  (was direct power; now bypass)
//   RELAY_FWD 18   → K1 forward direction relay
//   RELAY_REV 19   → K2 reverse direction relay
//   LIMIT_SWITCH_PIN 27, BUZZER_PIN 23, SDA 21, SCL 22  — all untouched
