//   6. PWM held at 255 (transistor still saturated, relay carries load)
//
// SOFT-STOP SEQUENCE (stopMotor):
//   1. RELAY_PWR (bypass K3) OFF first                (current to transistor)
//   2. Ramp PWM 255→0 over ~2.5 s                    (smooth current decay)
//   3. PWM = 0, direction relays OFF                  (fully off)
//
// ALL FIX-01…FIX-11 comments preserved verbatim.
// BUZZER: zero changes.
